首頁SARS研究SARS分子流行病學












				Molecular Epidemiology of SARS Coronavirus			


The epidemic of Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome (SARS) in Taiwan during 2003 had been reported 346 SARS cases to the World Health Organization. In this website, we developed a new method for the phylogenetic analysis to study the origin and dissemination of SARS CoV infection in Taiwan. The well alignment file of the reference sequences provided on the "SARS Alignment".
 

 











